living_together: What matters to me is that people can help to each other and that we can share goods.
decision_making: I think the best way is to come all together with ideas and downsize it to the best decision.
personal_contribution: I would like to contribute by sharing my time with the people in the community.

regime_of_sharing: ['Minimal/no shared spaces', 'Shared extra spaces (gardens, workshops, guest rooms, garage)']
living_together: What matters to me is to share time and activities together. Ideally also having similar values and interests in common with the people of the group. What also is very important is to manage the house tasks responsibly so that there are not discussions or misunderstandings due to this.
decision_making: I think that the best way is that everyone has a little responsibility and that everyone can negociate and finally agree on the rules. Probably by doing monthly meetings for the practicalities of the community.
personal_contribution: I would want to contribute by giving company and helping each other. As well, I would want to receive the same way. It is so much easier when you live with people that can help you emotionally but also in practically in daily tasks: groceries, cleaning, etc.

living_together: Be somewhat aligned on the values, understan each other and commit to the group. I believe this can be built with time with the correct people through activities together.
decision_making: Having an honest conversation on which everyone is honest about their opinions. Based on that try to take a decision, maybe using some voting system if not clear
personal_contribution: Everyday conversation, time to time activities and commitment to the decision taken as group

desired_location: Prefecture of Kyoto, little village, in the countryside
regime_of_sharing: ['Shared extra spaces (gardens, workshops, guest rooms, garage)']
living_together: Respetar los limites de cada uno. Somos vecinos, no familia, e igualmente hay que definir el grado de amistad. Respetar las normas establecidas por la comunidad.
decision_making: Reunion/junta, buzón/portal anonimo, roles diferenciados, un portavoz proactivo, evaluación interna de la gestión de la comunidad
personal_contribution: Crear un espacio seguro y cómodo, para familias y personas en periodo de desarrollo tanto familiar como personal, pudiendo favorecerse unos de los otros y ahorrar gastos
